  target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more about Dr. John</a></strong></p>
 <p>  Poster presentations and the opportunity for those interested in glo
 bal health throughout the university to network and share information wil
 l follow grand rounds.</p><p>  Global Health Scholars Day is open to anyo
